{"tid":2423243,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Sony 將逐步解散Japan Studio","createTime":"2021-02-25T20:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T01:56:27.000Z","uid":5320,"like":5,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"0d8322820213526467df815d6f7fe7bf59ac6bcf","tid":2423243,"uid":5320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T20:58:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.videogameschronicle.com/news/sources-playstation-is-winding-down-sony-japan-studio/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.videogameschronicle.com%2Fnews%2Fsources-playstation-is-winding-down-sony-japan-studio%2F&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd6y1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=d2444066\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.videogameschronicle.com/news/sources-playstation-is-winding-down-sony-japan-studio/</a><br />\n<br />\nBloodborne molamola<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&gt; 部分翻譯/業務員工留係ASOBI team (Astro's Playroom)<br />\n<br />\n&gt; 估計係將業務重心集中係加州<br />\n<br />\n&gt; 外山圭一郎, (Silent Hill, Siren, Gravity Rush) 創作人聯同幾個前Japan Studio 員工創立 Bokeh Game Studio, 整恐怖game<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YSkdD6S-YRE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYSkdD6S-YRE&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd6y1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=32b2b363\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YSkdD6S-YRE</a><br />\n<br />\n多個員工離開Japan Studio, 好多有份Bloodborne, Demon's Souls開發<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/giwamasa/status/1364776713280913412?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgiwamasa%2Fstatus%2F1364776713280913412%3Fs%3D20&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd6y1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=d47c5d9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgiwamasa%2Fstatus%2F1364776713280913412%3Fs%3D20&h=a83b4f70\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/giwamasa/status/1364776713280913412?s=20</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/teru_toriyama/status/1342002080462950400?s=20\" data-sr-ur